      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- User wants short url\n- API server picks ticket server\n    - server knows available range ids. (configuration or fixed)\n- API server selects one range at random\n- API server\n    - select te \"current\" of the range\n    - increments current by 1 if end != current",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- User wants short url\n- API server picks ticket server\n    - server knows available range ids. (configuration or fixed)\n- API server selects one range at random\n- API server\n    - select te \"current\" of the range\n    - increments current by 1 if end != current",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
