    {
      "id": "sxGnUDfEctTut0fta72oV",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3222.8857554819406,
      "y": 45618.81563570391,
      "width": 495,
      "height": 200,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bPr",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1321517539,
      "version": 467,
      "versionNonce": 1180568033,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776908631077,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "How are we are taking care of randomnes \n- we are picking one ticket server at random\n- From the ticket server we are picking one\n  range at random.\n- From that range we are picking currentValue\n  we are doing ++ in TRANSACTION like above.\n- that integer comes to API and then encoded \n   and stored as short_code i the URL DB",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "How are we are taking care of randomnes \n- we are picking one ticket server at random\n- From the ticket server we are picking one\n  range at random.\n- From that range we are picking currentValue\n  we are doing ++ in TRANSACTION like above.\n- that integer comes to API and then encoded \n   and stored as short_code i the URL DB",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "3liUwdbf-lHbTH8IKDs8b",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2081.112696994752,
      "y": 46371.42489953636,
      "width": 1210,
      "height": 125,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bPt",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1209393549,
      "version": 165,
      "versionNonce": 1573437615,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776908631077,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Exercise\n\n- implement the encoding scheme we discussed (from integer -> string, define custom map, encoding -> decoding)\n- explore analytics we can capture and how during short url hit\n- explore how exactly we share analytics data",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Exercise\n\n- implement the encoding scheme we discussed (from integer -> string, define custom map, encoding -> decoding)\n- explore analytics we can capture and how during short url hit\n- explore how exactly we share analytics data",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "N2yO5uQ1W_nNi2IC1dFko",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2476.528180235354,
      "y": 46648.26613693382,
      "width": 492.7998046875,
      "height": 35,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bPu",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1796155478,
      "version": 525,
      "versionNonce": 1657432662,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776397993528,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Designing PasteBin (github gist)",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Designing PasteBin (github gist)",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "hkK6gnwe_-_l9swEMfTZG",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2233.561703794924,
      "y": 46757.94582443382,
      "width": 759,
      "height": 225,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bPv",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 699994698,
      "version": 96,
      "versionNonce": 1198586305,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776518443876,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "\nPasteBin is an online platform that allows you to:\n - store any text file (content) → public to anyone\n - share it with anyone (publicly or secretly) → anyone with the link\n - set an expiration for auto deletion\n - URL generated for a paste is unique\n - file stored can be long (but not huge) (10MB max)\n - one who created the paste can edit it as well\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "\nPasteBin is an online platform that allows you to:\n - store any text file (content) → public to anyone\n - share it with anyone (publicly or secretly) → anyone with the link\n - set an expiration for auto deletion\n - URL generated for a paste is unique\n - file stored can be long (but not huge) (10MB max)\n - one who created the paste can edit it as well\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "zKbBD794PAnpjxiG4nS5A",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2239.763363951174,
      "y": 47021.990135957254,
      "width": 477.3998107910156,
      "height": 35,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#e03131",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bPw",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 995725633,
      "version": 600,
      "versionNonce": 1604470991,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1776518459533,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Where should we store the file?",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Where should we store the file?",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "d4OO4dTPXqkCnIfP-ZK6i",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2277.815610044924,
      "y": 47094.953514863504,
      "width": 605,
      "height": 375,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bPx",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 972810575,
      "version": 115,
      "versionNonce": 831209409,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1776518615233,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "We have two options: **Database or Blob store like S3**\n\nTo decide which one, let’s crunch some numbers\n\n - max size per file = **10MB**\n - say #writes = **10M per month**\n\nTotal storage req = 10M × 10MB\n                  = 10,000,000 × 10,000,000 B\n                  = **100TB (per month)\n\nTypical write to read = 1:50\n\nTotal data read = 5PB (Bandwidth required) (per month)\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "We have two options: **Database or Blob store like S3**\n\nTo decide which one, let’s crunch some numbers\n\n - max size per file = **10MB**\n - say #writes = **10M per month**\n\nTotal storage req = 10M × 10MB\n                  = 10,000,000 × 10,000,000 B\n                  = **100TB (per month)\n\nTypical write to read = 1:50\n\nTotal data read = 5PB (Bandwidth required) (per month)\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "INMlpeLlZZbG8F2R9ijQN",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2279.424985044924,
      "y": 47485.75112228538,
      "width": 539,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "bPy",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1660087137,
      "version": 189,
      "versionNonce": 619277185,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1776518653684,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Since data is huge & per file size is long enough\nthere is no rationale to store this on a database",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Since data is huge & per file size is long enough\nthere is no rationale to store this on a database",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "poWVjWIdcnFK4w0nrXeoO",
      "type": "text",
